snippet.title: Oops! No Brakes!: More Oops Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer for "Oops! No Breaks!: More Oops!", a game originally created for the Kenney Jam 2021, now receiving a significant post-jam update! Available to play now (for free!) at https://thejaspel.itch.io/oops-no-brakes.

Programming & Design by TheJaspel
Itch.io: https://thejaspel.itch.io
Twitter: https://twitter.com/thejaspel1

Music (and trailer) by Zachary Pinkham
Website: https://www.zacharypinkham.com
Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/zachary-pinkham
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/zacharypink...
Twitter: https://twitter.com/zachpinkham
Itch.io: https://zacharypinkham.itch.io
